_chem_comp_bond.comp_id
_chem_comp_bond.atom_id_1
_chem_comp_bond.atom_id_2
_chem_comp_bond.value_order
FOR "C" "O"  DOUB
FOR "C" "H1" SING
FOR "C" "H2" SING
